			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">OP: there is a Wiki page on this subject.  It speaks in &quot;general tone&quot; for development, so that the concept/implementation can be understood:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/The_frame_and_NMIs">https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/The_frame_and_NMIs</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Section &quot;When to Turn Off PPU, NMIs&quot; may be relevant to your interests (don't let the section title mislead you), but the entire page seems highly relevant to what's being discussed.</div>

